All Classes

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Block
    Class of block building infrastructure of level, such as unbreakable walls types stored in @id field class extends Rectangle class default type of block is empty block Block almost always have @Tile size
    Character
    Class representing player's character class extends class @Creatures 4 different skins for character each has size of standard @Tile contains information about lives and score of the player
    Component  
    Creatures
    parent class for all 'alive' objects such as character and enemies stores information about dimensions of creature and his localisation (in double)
    Enemy
    Class of enemy mobs class extends class @Creatures 3 different types of enemies each has size of standard @Tile
    Level
    Class loads level from file to two dimensions char table and from this table loads level to two dimensions Block table.
    Tile
    Class storing coded names of blocks, character's skins and other items also stores size of standard tile in game also stores buffered images of each item in game loaded from .png files in "/res/..." folder
